  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at the 6th level, when you would cast a Taijutsu with the <em>Combo</em> keyword, you can cast a Bukijutsu with the <em>Finisher</em> keyword using your taijutsu ability modifier. The Bukijutsu cast counts as a Taijutsu for the purpose of Taijutsu Specialist feature interactions. You can only cast 1 Finisher per turn.</p><p>When you cast a bukijutsu with the Finisher keyword, you can spend Martial Die equal to the rank of the juttsu to add your Taijutsu Specialist level to the first damage roll. <em><strong>(D/C-Rank: 1, B/A-Rank: 2, S- Rank: 3)</strong></em></p>",
